<br>
Hmm well, not truth.<br>
<br>
Flash of light:When it's cast on the target, the target will keep fighting if the person/pet with the most aggro is in melee range. If the person or pet with the most aggro is not in melee range, the target will run/walk away in the direction facing.<br>
<br>
That's why it is used for aggro kiting as well.<br>
Sure you can get loads of adds in this way, but that spell is very usefull.<br>
