<br>
Another note about blinding: when characters are blind, apparently they are deaf, numb, and mute as well.  Why do I say this?  Because the cheap shortcut used by the designers turns off your dialog box too... you can't hear, you cant really talk, you can't tell you are being hit or if you are hitting.  The message boxes should be in place still, visible on top of the darkness because it's the only way you interact with the world.  You shouldn't be able to see, but you should still be able to tell if you are hitting or not, if you are hit, if your freinds talk to you, etc. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=retrievil>Retrievil</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 81<br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/3/03 10:26 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: useless spell</span><hr size=1> The illusion tree line has recently been changed to add 5 hps a tick regen and it stacks with regeneration and cloro etc.  I gave my GF (shes a druid ieeee!!!) a Maple Leaf Mask and she uses it all the time when recovering from a hit or two when quadding.  Cast regen ... click mask ... full hp by the time shes fm.  It does save her a bit of healing and every little bit adds up to more xp overall.  Plus its fun to cast it in gfay and buff noobs.  A TREE JUST GAVE ME SOW!<br>
<br>
 My vote for most worthless spell is the necromancer 'scent' debuff line.  It debuffs FR PR and DR.  Problem is ... all of our FR dots are basically irresistable unless the mob is 100% FR, we dont cast disease usually because they all suck until Dark Plague (which again is nearly unresistable).  Poison, mighgt be useful but, you will only cast it once during a fight.  Cost you more to debuff then cast than just to recast on a resist. The main problem tho is there is no MR reduction.  The only resist that necros rely on.  If we cant land our magic spells, we probably wont be fighting it for xp.  Then you have the fact that its almost impossible to land because its MR based .... you see where Im getting to dont you?  Useless spells, all of em. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.shaw.ca/jpew/sig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
